strings: <Cap><leader> discovers a new recipe for the alchemy pot!
<Cap><string_1> <equal> <Cap><string_2> + <Cap><string_3>
<Cap><string_1> <equal> <Cap><string_2> + <Cap><string_3> + <Cap><string_4>
<se_high>*: Tweet tweet tweet!
<se_def>*: Woof woof WOOF!
<se_low>*: Ah, welcome! Bless you, my child.
<se_low>*: You may not believe it to look at me now, but in my younger days I was quite a looker. People used to call me the ‘sexy sister’!
<se_low>*: I wonder if there's anything I can do to help you today (cough). Let's see...
<se_def>*: You can get loads of mushrooms in the woods 'round here. My mum can't get enough of 'em.
<se_def>*: I often come here to pick a few dozen, though it's a bit of a trek from town.
<se_high>*: Cheep cheep cheep!
<se_def>*: Ruff ruff RUFF!
The horse seems to be enjoying its grass.
<se_low>*: You can get hold of some really good rock salt down there, you know.
<se_low>*: I've been digging it out and selling it to earn a living.
<se_low>*: What's a thing like that doing in the middle of nowhere?
<se_low>*: Ah! <IF_SOLO>A traveller<ELSE_NOT_SOLO>Travellers<ENDIF_SOLO>! Have you seen that strange-looking rock formation over there?
<se_low>*: Look! If you squint, you'll see it. It's shaped just like a ship.
<se_low>*: There's no way there'd be a ship all the way out here, though... It really is a puzzle!
<se_low>*: That rock formation over there looks so much like a ship. I'm intrigued!
<se_low>*: If I didn't have to work, I'd go over and take a closer look.
<se_high>*: Coo coo!
<se_def>*: (Whimper whimper)
The horse is pawing the ground, looking for some grass to eat.
<se_low>*: It's about time we set off to peddle our wares, but my partner doesn't seem to want to leave.
<se_low>*: What a pain!
<se_low>*: There was a strange-looking rock formation over there before! Where's it gone!?
<se_low>*: There's no way a huge thing like that could just disappear. This is really strange!
<se_high>*: Caw caw!
<se_def>*: Grrr!
<se_low>*: Gurrrr... Urrr...
<se_low>*: Rock...formation... How... Urrr...
<se_high>*: Sometimes we join together and make one giant slime! It's really good fun!
<se_high>*: But we didn't reckon on getting stuck down a well like that! Thanks for helping us out! Well done! (Slurp)
<se_high>*: (Slurp, slurp...)
<se_high>*: I won't be turning into a king slime ever again! (Slurp)
<se_high>*: Have you been across the plain yet? There's something really cool down there!
<se_high>*: There's this really old ship! It was even bigger than us when we were one huge slime!
<se_high>*: You're a bit of a weird shape, aren't you? Nowhere near as wonderfully wobbly as we are!
<se_high>*: If you go down the mountain, you'll find this really big ship. Watch how you go though.
<se_high>*: There's a load of bad monsters on the way down and nowhere to rest when you do finally get to the bottom!
<se_high>*: Seeing as you helped us and everything, maybe I'll tell you a little secret.
<se_high>*: If you mix two agility rings with something really precious, you can make a meteorite bracer.
<se_high>*: I wonder what that really precious something is... (Slurp)
<se_high>*: Humans are nicer than I thought! Thanks for helping us out! (Slurp)
<se_low>*: Ah, welcome! Bless you, my child.
<se_low>*: You may not believe it to look at me now, but in my younger days I was quite a looker. People used to call me the ‘sexy sister’!
<se_low>*: Anyway, what can I do for you today?
<se_def>*: Grrrrr... Woof!
<se_low>*: Every day I vow that tomorrow will be the day I set off again. Huh...
<se_low>*: Rock...formation... How... Urrr...
